name: My first travel
description:
Was almost a dream, 
but it was better because it was true reality.
It was my first time that i took pictures. I really didnt understand what was going on with me, I was enjoying it so much that i felt strange.
Today I am very grateful to young Juan.

That one was my first time travelling with my friends.
We were 18, nothing like fly with our backpack and realize how is to travel.


I share this picture for the dreamers ones.

Picture from Tilcara, Jujuy, Argentina.
